title: #92Noon! Wobby/Fleck/Gleem
description: It's the first day of #92Noon at the Fair! Wobby swings by the booth to talk Vikings, Gopher Football Head Coach P.J. Fleck joins the program to talk about his team, and Aaron Gleeman closes out the show talking Twins and more!
